  "instructions": [
    "Cube the tofu and set aside.",
    "Blanch the bamboo shoots, carrot, spinach, and soybean sprouts in boiling water for 2 minutes then plunge into ice water.",
    "Heat the lazy-susan-spinner with vegetable stock and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add soy sauce, mustard, sesame oil, salt, and pepper, then stir to combine.",
    "Add the ramen noodles and cook for 4 minutes until al dente.",
    "Fold in the blanched vegetables and tofu, cooking for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Slice the green onion and sprinkle over the ramen.",
    "Garnish with a sheet of nori before serving."
